# Patches

 + exresize

    Resize, move and temporarily maximize clients using your keyboard.

 + switchstack

    Switch between cycling through floating and tiled clients.

 + combo 

    Selecting several tags by pressing corresponing keys at the same time.

 + float border color 

    Specify colors for borders when clients are floating.

 + urgentborder

    Highlights urgent borders in specified colors

 + pertag - not working

    Different layout, mwfact, barpos and nmaster per tag

 + spawn cwd

    Spawn applications copies cwd from the client that currently has focus.

 + statusallmons

    Draw the statusbar on all monitors

 + systray

    Adds a systray on the right side of the bar.

 + viewontag

    Switches to the tag where you move a client.
